Peanut Butter Cookie Recipe 
Rombauer, Irma S, Marion R. Becker, Ethan Becker, and Maria Guarnaschelli. Joy of Cooking. New York: Scribner, 1997. Print.
Ingredients 
1/2 cup butter or shortening
1/2 cup packed Brown sugar
1/2 cup gran. sugar
1 egg
1 cup peanut butter
1/2 tsp salt
1/2 tsp baking soda
1/2 tsp vanilla
1 add 1 to 1 1/2 cup flour

Instructions 
beat butter/shortening until creamy
sift and add rest of ingredients 
roll into small balls. place in greased cookie sheet. press flat with a fork and bake 10..12 min.
bake 375Â°F
